original: Kjeilström, Ernst Vilhelm, komminister, Hångsdala, f. 9/3/06 i Norsjö, Västerb. 1., av Vilhelm K. o. Hulda Teresia Carlsson. — Stud:ex. i Gbg 27, teol. fil. ex. 28, tcol. kand. samt prakt. teol. prov 36, prästv. f. Skara stift 37. Tjg. i Hjälstad 37 samt s. pastiadj. i Råda, tjg. i N. Härene, Odensåker, Otterstad, V. Tunhem, Gustav Adolf, Stenstorp o. Varv, kom-min. i Hångsdala sed. 46.
translated: Kjeilström, Ernst Vilhelm, assistant minister, Hångsdala, born on March 9, 1906 in Norsjö, Västerbotten County, son of Vilhelm K. and Hulda Teresia Carlsson. — Completed studies in Gothenburg in 1927, theology degree in 1928, practical theological examination in 1936, ordained priest in Skara Diocese in 1937. Served in Hjälstad in 1937, assistant minister in Råda, served in N. Härene, Odensåker, Otterstad, V. Tunhem, Gustav Adolf, Stenstorp and Varv, minister in Hångsdala since 1946.
